# kIOPropertyProductSerialNumberKey | Apple Developer Documentation

- [ DriverKit ](/documentation/driverkit)

-  kIOPropertyProductSerialNumberKey 

Macro# kIOPropertyProductSerialNumberKey

DriverKitiOSiPadOSmacOS

```
#define kIOPropertyProductSerialNumberKey
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/driverkit/kiopropertyproductserialnumberkey#Discussion)

This key is used to indicate the card serial number ID.

Requirement: Mandatory

Example:



```
 
 
 <dict>
    <key>Card Characteristics</key>
    <dict>
   	 <key>Product Name</key>
   	 <string>SD32G</string>
   	 <key>Product Revision Level</key>
   	 <string>1.0</string>
   	 <key>Card Type</key>
   	 <string>SDHC</string>
   	 <key>Serial Number</key>
   	 <data>0045ff</data>
    </dict>
 </dict>
 
 

```
